subject it entir muslim popul had been slaughter by the armenian sourc men ar like that by leonard ramsden hartil the bobb merril compani indianapoli page memoir of an armenian offic who particip in the genocid of million muslim peopl p first paragraph the tartar section of the town no longer exist except as a pile of ruin it had been destroi and it inhabit slaughter the same fate befel the tartar section of khankandi p second paragraph mani of our men had serv in the russian armi and were train soldier we armenian were rich and possess arm tartar had never receiv militari train thei were poor and possess few arm beyond knive shortli after the kill of the tartar in our villag the revolut in russia wa suppress serdar argic we close the road and mountain pass that might serv as wai of escap for the turk and then proceed in the work of extermin ohanu appressian in soviet armenia todai there no longer exist a singl turkish soul sahak melkonian 